{"word":"Firstborn","slug":"firstborn","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Firstborn</b> Of man and beast, reserved to Himself by God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=13&verse=2'>Exo 13:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=13&verse=16'>Exo 13:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=22&verse=30'>Exo 22:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=20'>Exo 34:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=27&verse=26'>Lev 27:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=13'>Num 3:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=8&verse=18'>Num 8:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=15&verse=23'>Deu 15:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=36'>Neh 10:36</a><br/> Redemption of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=13&verse=13'>Exo 13:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=20'>Exo 34:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=27&verse=27'>Lev 27:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=51'>Num 3:51</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=17'>Num 18:17</a><br/> Levites taken instead of firstborn of the families of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=12'>Num 3:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=45'>Num 3:45</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=8&verse=18'>Num 8:18</a><br/> Of Egyptians, slain<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=11&verse=5'>Exo 11:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=12'>Exo 12:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=29'>Exo 12:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=13&verse=15'>Exo 13:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=33&verse=4'>Num 33:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=78&verse=51'>Psa 78:51</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=105&verse=36'>Psa 105:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=136&verse=10'>Psa 136:10</a><br/> Of idolaters, sacrificed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=20&verse=26'>Eze 20:26</a><br/> Birthright of:<br/> - Authority over younger members of the household<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=4&verse=7'>Gen 4:7</a> <br/> - A double portion of inheritance<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=21&verse=17'>Deu 21:17</a> <br/> - Royal succession<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=21&verse=3'>2Ch 21:3</a> <br/> - Honorable distinction of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=22'>Exo 4:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=89&verse=27'>Psa 89:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=31&verse=9'>Jer 31:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=8&verse=29'>Rom 8:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=1&verse=15'>Col 1:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=1&verse=6'>Heb 1:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=12&verse=23'>Heb 12:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=1&verse=5'>Rev 1:5</a> <br/> - Sold by Esau<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=34'>Gen 25:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27&verse=36'>Gen 27:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=9&verse=13'>Rom 9:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=12&verse=16'>Heb 12:16</a> <br/> - Forfeited by Reuben<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=49&verse=4'>Gen 49:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=2'>1Ch 5:2</a> <br/> - Set aside:<br/> b That of Manasseh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=48&verse=20'>Gen 48:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=1'>1Ch 5:1</a><br/> b That of Adonijah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=15'>1Ki 2:15</a><br/> b That of Hosah's son<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=26&verse=10'>1Ch 26:10</a><br/><a href='S:Birthright'>Birthright</a>"}]}